 hard and soft potentials, and we further justify\nthe property of propagation of regularity of solutions in the spatial\nvariables.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 27 Apr 2019 01:44:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-18"}
