ifting concepts. The\nproposed filter validates its efficiency and feasibility by substantially\nimproving the classification accuracy and reducing the false positive error of\nmisclassifying legitimate e-mail as spam.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 27 Apr 2019 07:00:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-30"}
